{"title":"我本可以忍受黑暗，如果我未曾见过光明","uid":"b7bc0822d26e4c0f7b72909cbc2af24b","slug":"金句","date":"2021-09-22T17:13:31.000Z","updated":"2021-10-04T11:09:05.050Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/金句.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/img/cover/jinju.jpeg","content":"<h2 id=\"金句分享\"><a href=\"#金句分享\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"金句分享\"></a><center>金句分享</h2><center>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"Had-I-not-seen-the-sun\"><a href=\"#Had-I-not-seen-the-sun\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Had I not seen the sun\"></a>Had I not seen the sun</h2><h2 id=\"I-could-have-borne-the-shade\"><a href=\"#I-could-have-borne-the-shade\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"I could have borne the shade\"></a>I could have borne the shade</h2><h2 id=\"But-Light-a-newer-Wilderness\"><a href=\"#But-Light-a-newer-Wilderness\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"But Light a newer Wilderness\"></a>But Light a newer Wilderness</h2><h2 id=\"My-Wilderness-has-made\"><a href=\"#My-Wilderness-has-made\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"My Wilderness has made\"></a>My Wilderness has made</h2><pre><code>                --Emily Dickinson\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>译文</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">译文一\n\n（江枫&#x2F;译）\n我本可以忍受黑暗\n如果我不曾见过太阳\n然而阳光已使我的荒凉\n成为更新的荒凉 \n\n\n译文二\n假如我没有见过太阳\n我也许会忍受黑暗；\n可如今，太阳把我的寂寞\n照耀得更加荒凉 <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>大言不惭，班门弄斧，我来译一译，献丑了</p></blockquote>\n<p>假如我未曾看见光明</p>\n<p>我本可安于黑暗</p>\n<p>然光明咫尺</p>\n<p>身影渐长</p>\n<hr>\n<p>不过我喜欢的是前两句。<br>如果没有后两句，我认为作者后面毕生是去追求光明去了，而不是说当光明到来的时候，会把自己显现的更黑。后两句的是悲观的和消极的。</p>\n<hr>\n<pre><code>                       W 等待 A   i    t\n</code></pre>\n","text":"金句分享 Had I not seen the sunI could have borne the shadeBut Light a newer WildernessMy Wilderness has made --Emily Dickinson 译文 译文一 （江枫&#x2F;...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":433,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"其他","slug":"其他","count":37,"path":"api/categories/其他.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"金句分享","slug":"金句分享","count":1,"path":"api/tags/金句分享.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%87%91%E5%8F%A5%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">金句分享</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Had-I-not-seen-the-sun\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Had I